column5: Hi,me and the gf and some frineds might be staying at one of these lakes in the summer for a long weekend and was wondering if anyone here has been to any of these lakes or heard anything about them? would love a heads up
Jack lake in Apsley?  Great fishing and some pretty awesome private cottages for rent. There is also Jacks lake lodge and a few campgrounds.
Hey bud, pm me. Jack lake at burk falls, right?I only shore fished it and caught a few pike and bass,nothing huge, but satisifying. AS for the others There is another  Pm me and ill tell you. cheers
I hope that that helped you.and if Im correct, 21 days and no camping fees, maybe a fire permit
